{{Infobox sport governing body |name = Australian Sport Aviation Confederation |abbrev = ASAC |logo = |logosize = 225px |sport = [[Air sports]] |category = |image = |caption = |jurisdiction = [[Australia]] |founded = {{Start date|2007}} |aff = [[Fédération Aéronautique Internationale]] |affdate = 2007 |region = |regionyear = |headquarters = Melbourne, Victoria |location = |president = |chairman = |chairperson = |chair = |chiefexec = |vicepresident = |director = |secretary = |coach = |womenscoach = |key staff = |operating income = |sponsor = |year closed = |replaced = |prevfounded = |url = http://www.asac.asn.au/ |countryflag = Australia }}
'''Australian Sport Aviation Confederation''' is the [[Sport governing body|governing body]] for the [[sport]] of [[Air sports]] in Australia.
