The '''Ethiopia Fed Cup team''' represents [[Ethiopia]] in [[Fed Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Ethiopian Tennis Federation]]. They have not competed since [[1998 Fed Cup|1998]].
==History== Ethiopia competed in its first Fed Cup in [[1996 Fed Cup|1996]], and also competed in [[1997 Fed Cup|1997]] and [[1998 Fed Cup|1998]]. They have lost all 13 of their ties to date.
