{{Infobox Athleticrace | bgcolour = #74C365 | image = | imagesize = 240px | caption = | date = September | location = [[Lycia]], [[Turkey]] | type = Multiday trail | distance = | est = {{start date and age|2010|10|11}} | sponsor = | record = {{unbulleted list|men's: 29:29:42 (2011)|women's: 38:43:57 (2012)}} | homepage = http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/EN/ }} {{Location map+ | Turkey | width = 275 | float = | border = | caption = Start and finish locations of Lycian Way Ultramarathon. | alt = | relief = yes | AlternativeMap = | overlay_image = | places = <!-- Start at Ölüdeniz --> {{Location map~ | Turkey | label = Start | label_size = | position = left | background = | mark = Athletics pictogram.svg | marksize = 15 | link = | lat_deg = 36 |lat_min = 33 |lat_sec = 20 |lat_dir = N | lon_deg = 29 |lon_min = 06 |lon_sec = 26 |lon_dir = E }} <!-- Finish at Antalya --> {{Location map~ | Turkey | label = Finish | label_size = | position = | background = | mark = Athletics pictogram.svg | marksize = 15 | link = | lat_deg = 36 |lat_min = 53 |lat_sec = 09 |lat_dir = N | lon_deg = 30 |lon_min = 40 |lon_sec = 08 |lon_dir = E }} }} [[File:Likya yolus.jpg|thumb|275px|Trail signs on the Lycian Way.]] '''Lycian Way Ultramarathon''' ({{lang-tr|Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu}}, shortly LYUM) is an international [[multiday race|multiday]] [[trail running]] [[ultramarathon]] event that takes place across the ancient [[Lycia]]n region in southwestern [[Turkey]]. The event is run around {{convert|220|-|240|km|mi|abbr=on}} of the {{convert|509|km|mi|abbr=on}} long historical [[Lycian Way]] eastwards from [[Fethiye]] to [[Antalya]] in six days. The elevation of the route varies between sea level and {{convert|800|m|ft|abbr=on}}.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/TR/?page=rota-100 |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=Rota |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref><ref name="lyumh">{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/TR/?page=hakkinda-97 |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=Hakkında |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref> The Lycian Way Ultramarathon was established in 2010 taking place on October 11–17.<ref name="lyum10">{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/TR/?page=lyum-2010-53 |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=LYUM 2010 |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref>
Changing ground conditions such as sandy and rocky trails, [[dirt road]]s, slippery terrain in conifer forests and steep slopes make the ultramarathon extremely difficult.<ref name="lyumh"/>
[[File:Map of Lycian way.jpg|thumb|275px|Map of the Lycian Way.]] The route starts at [[Ölüdeniz]] in Fethiye district of [[Muğla Province]]. Following the [[Turkish Riviera]] coastline, it passes through [[List of Lycian place names|Sidyma]] and then in [[Antalya Province]] the places [[Kaş]], [[Kaleköy, Kaş|Simena]], [[Finike]], [[Olympos (Lycia)|Olympos]] and [[Phaselis]]. The race ends in [[Antalya]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/images/slider_images/4.jpg |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=Route map |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref>
The fourth edition of the event in 2013 was cancelled because many foreign ultra runners stayed away or annulled their entry due to perceived risks in connection with the [[2013 protests in Turkey]] and [[2012 Syrian–Turkish border clashes]]. The cancellation caused reaction by local athletes, who had already arranged their training, holiday and airline tickets in accordance with the race term.<ref name="h1">{{cite news |url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/24650585.asp |newspaper=[[Hürriyet]] |title=Likya Maratonu neden iptal edildi |author=Ataer, Kazım |date=2013-09-05 |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref>
==Winners== '''Key:''' {{legend2|#A9F5A9|'''Course record'''|border=solid 1px #AAAAAA}} {| class="wikitable sortable" style="text-align:center" |- !Year !class=unsortable |Men's winner !Time ([[hour|h]]:[[minute|m]]:[[second|s]]) !class=unsortable |Women's winner !Time ([[hour|h]]:[[minute|m]]:[[second|s]]) |- |2010<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/TR/?page=genel-siralama-176 |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=LYUM 2010-Genel Sıralama |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref> |align=left |{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Mustafa Kızıltaş]] |31:52:11 |align=left |{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Aylin Savacı Armador]] |48:36:57 |- |2011<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/TR/?lym=genel-siralama-bireysel-136&siralama |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=LYUM 2011-Genel Sıralama (Bireysel) |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref> |align=left |{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Mustafa Kızıltaş]] |bgcolor=#A9F5A9 |29:29:42 |align=left |{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Elena Polyakova]] |39:25:20 |- |2012<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.likyayoluultramaratonu.com/TR/?page=genel-siralama-170 |publisher=Likya Yolu Ultramaratonu |title=LYUM 2012-Genel Sıralama |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-11-27 }}</ref> |align=left |{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Faruk Kar]] |32:35:08 |align=left |{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Elena Polyakova]] |bgcolor=#A9F5A9 |38:43:57 |- |2013<ref name="h1"/> |colspan=4 |''Cancelled'' |- |''2014'' |align=left |{{flagicon|}} | |align=left |{{flagicon|}} | |}
