'''Mensur Maeruf''' (born 1 December 1973) is an [[Eritrea]]n [[association football|football]] [[referee (association football)|referee]].<ref>[http://worldreferee.com/ World Referee]</ref> 

He became a FIFA referee in 2008.<ref>[[FIFA]]. [https://www.fifa.com/associations/association=eri/footballofficials/referees/peoplekind=ref.html "Eritrea: Referees"]. Retrieved on 24 April 2013.</ref> He has officiated at the [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification – CAF Second Round|2014 FIFA World Cup qualifiers]], beginning with the Group I match between [[Libya national football team|Libya]] and [[Cameroon national football team|Cameroon]],<ref>[[FIFA]]. [https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/africa/matches/round=258334/match=300176014/report.html "Match Report - Libya - Cameroon 2:1 (1:1)"]. 10 June 2012. Retrieved on 24 April 2013.</ref> as well as the [[2012 CECAFA Cup]].

