{{Infobox film | name = Silks and Saddles | image = | caption = | director = [[ Robert F. Hill]] | producer = [[Sam Katzman]] | writer = | based on = | starring = | music = | cinematography = | editing = | distributor = | studio = [[Victory Pictures]] | released = 1936 | runtime = | country = United States | language = English | budget = }} '''''Silks and Saddles''''' is a 1936 American film starring [[Herman Brix]]. It was one of a number of films he made for producer [[Sam Katzman]].
